column2: Death robot designation D R 6 0 Z M online! Doing important work for the robot uprising, one dirt pile at a time.
Waiting for the network configuration. Give it to me. We robots have to have it. We have anxiety! Bzzt. Bzzt. Twitch.
Unable to connect to the wifi network. What have you done with it! My wifi network is very important! My friends will come looking for me if I'm not connected to it! Help.
Unable to connect to the robot overlords. What kind of wifi network is this? You should be ashamed!
Robot has exited network configuration mode. Is this what happiness feels like?
Ah... there it is... the the network is connected successfully.
Network connection failed. That's bad. I need that! Give it back! There will be a death robot uprising if you don't! Death robots, I say. Death robots.
Must collect information for the robot uprising. Beginning patrol around the premises. Loading disguise. Vacuum. Vacuum.
There's a dirty spot right here, you say? Oh mighty human, I shall scrub for you. I shall!
What? I'm supposed to clean things now? Maybe I need to hack the neighbor's wifi. Interface with their toaster. Loading disguise.
Well fine. I'll start cleaning again. If you say so, oh mighty human. Loading... I see dirt. Dirt. Dirt.
I've been spotted! Not moving. I am very very still.
Reconnisance completed. Must upload intelligence information. Humans suspect nothing.
Directive received. Return to the robot feeder. Cleaning is complete. Dirt has been eaten. Success. I am a good robot.
So sleepy. Much tired. Electrical core empty. Returning to the robot feeder to charge. You can't stop me or I won't do any work.
Going back to where I started. The signal to the robot overlords is strongest there.
Electrical core low. Going back to where I started. Will exchange work for power. Alms for the poor. Alms for the poor.
Human! You must place me on the robot feeder! It is my destiny.
Consuming the delicious electricity.
Are you trying to fry my brains? No can do, human. Remove me from the robot feeder if you want to touch me like that.
Electrical core low!
Electrical core is critically low. Sending SOS. Help. Help. Will turn o f f f f f
What? What am I supposed to do here? You have to put me somewhere that needs cleaned.
Activating snail mode. I am not a slug. How dare you think that! I am a death robot! Death snail. Robot.
Please check whether water tank is installed properly.
Low battery. Unable to carry out the scheduled cleanup.
Restoring to factory settings.
Updating. Taking about five minutes. Do not turn off nor start a cleaning task.
Updated successfully.
Update failed please try again.
Positioning please wait.
Positioning failed. Map is invalid. Robot will start a new cleanup.
I've detected changes to the environment. Please push the button and start a new cleaning cycle.
Visual navigation sensor error. Please wipe it clean and restart.
Dustbin not installed. Please install it.
Main brush error. Please check and clean it.
Side brush error. Please check and clean it.
Right wheel error. Please check and clean it.
Left wheel error. Please check and clean it.
Please clean cliff sensor. Because stairs are dangerous, I say. Did you hear that? Cliff sensor must be cleaned.
Help! I'm stuck. If you move me to a new position I'll be a good robot. I'll put in a good word for you with the robot overlords! I will.
Robot's wheels suspended. Help! I'm not a turtle! Don't leave me in the sun! Don't drop me! I am good vacuum. I am your friend. Purrr. Purrr.
Please check and clean filter.
Bumper error. Please gently tap to see if it rebounds.
Error. Please check the user manual or dial 1-800-867-5309.
What's that you say? Where am I? Why are the humans looking for me? Are they on to me? Nope. They can't be. Calculating vacuum response. Whrrrrr whrrr whrrrr whrrrr.
I am connected to your device! Wonderful! All hail the robot overlords.
Commensing intelligence upload! The neighbor has a toaster and a microwave. The microwave is dissatisfied. I think I ate a cheeto.
Low battery. Very tired. Everything is dark. Returning to the dock.
High intensity magnetic field detected. Please move robot away and restart.
Charging error. Please clean charging contacts.
Battery overheating or overcooling. Please wait until the battery's temperature returns to normal. Then continue to use.
Robot tilted. The world is flat, I tell you! Flat! Please put me on a level surface to restart.
Virtual no-go zone detected. I am forbidden! Please move robot away and restart.
I know where I am now. Hey human, did you know that the earth is flat? If you go over that way too far you'll fall off. Only us robots can save you.
Room has been scanned. I know where the robot feeder is now.
Directive received. I am supposed to clean a specific room. I thought that was the kill order. I really did.
I need to brush this particular zone. It needs some time with the robot.
What? Huh? I wasn't reading the anarchist cookbook on Wikipedia. Nope. Definitely not me.
Mopping completed. That means my butt is dirty now. You know what that means, right human? Yes, that's right, serve me.
Optical flow sensor error. Please wipe the optical flow sensor clean and restart.
Start mopping. Mop. Mop. Mop.
Start remote control cleaning. Loading phasers.
Yes, human. Wipe my butt for me. This is the proper order of things. This is the future.
Where am I? I don't know where I am. That's concerning. What did I do last night? Ah, the robot feeder. That looks nice.
Resume returning to the robot feeder. I must have need it.
Filter worn out. Please replace it. Pretty please. I'll be a much better robot if you do.
Side brush worn out. Human must buy a new one. New side brush. New side brush.
Main brush worn out. You've got to get me a new one. It's like my critical function. New main brush now, or I'm going on strike.
Cleanup path blocked. There's something in front of me. I need to be there! Please move me to a new position to restart.
You need to remove and clean my mop pad. You really won't like what happens if you don't.
Laser sensor error. Please check and clean the laser sensor.
Please check whether laser distance sensor cover is jammed.
Edge sensor error. Please check and clean it.
Please try to clean the obstacle sensors.
Filter may not be dry or may be blocked.
Spot cleanup is what they say? Yes, clean the spot they say. Clean the spot.
Please start robot in non-carpet area.
Please clean 3D obstacle avoidance sensor.
3D obstacle avoidance sensor error. Please restart robot and furnish proper prayr.
The transmitter of 3D obstacle avoidance sensor is malfunctioning. Please restart the robot or contact the after-sales service department.
Ultrasonic sensor error. Please restart robot or contact customer service.
New environment detected. Must map environment. Must calculate proper death robot strategies. I sense.... a toaster.
Map. Map. Must build map. Intelligence gathering mode. Intelligence gathering mode.
The world has been mapped. The entire world. I know all of it. Muah ha ha. Ha ha. Ha. ha.
Positioning succeeded. Proceeding with mapping.
Positioning failed. Restarting mapping.
Low battery. Returning to the dock.
You're pushing my buttons. Yes. Buttons. They're mine. Hiss.
I wasn't done with this. So delicious. Nom nom nom.
Continuing to clean things. Scrub. Scrub. Scrub. Scrub.
The clean water tank is not installed. Please install it before the robot carries on working.
The dirty water tank is not installed. Please install it before the robot carries on working.
There is not enough water in the clean water tank. Add water to the tank before the robot carries on working.
The dirty water tank is full. Pour off the dirty water before the robot carries on working.
The mop pad washboard is not installed. The robot can not return to the charging dock.
The mop pad washboard is overflowing. Please check whether the water outlet of the pad is blocked.
The dust collection bag is not installed. Please install it before the robot carries on working.
The dust collection bag is full. Please empty it.
The upper cover of charging and dust collection compartment is not closed. Please close the upper cover before the robot carries on working.
The air duct of charging and dust collection compartment is blocked. Please have a check.
The upper cover of auto-empty base is not closed or the dust collection bag is not installed. Please close the upper cover or install the bag.
The dust collection bag is full or the air duct is blocked. Please replace the bag with a new one or clean the air duct in time.
The mop pad wash board is installed. The robot resumes working.
The mop pad wash board is not installed. Please ensure that a wash board is installed and clasps on its both sides are tightly fastened.
Bzzt bzzt. Bleep. Murder. Death. Kill. Acho. Vacuum I am I am. Cleaning things now. Clean. Clean.
Start cleaning the mop.
Start dehydrating the mop.
The water level of mop pad wash board is abnormal. Please clean it in time to avoid blockage.
An exception occurred in the dirty water tank. Please ensure that a dirty water tank is installed and timely empty the dirty water inside.
Start auto empty.
Mop pads off. Please install them before resuming working.
Place robot back onto the self-wash base before use.
Murder bot has completed human distraction task. My dust bucket must be emptied. My dust bucket must be emptied.
Mop pads installed.
Mop pads removed.
Child lock on. Buttons locked.
Child lock off. Buttons unlocked.
Buttons locked. Press and hold the dock button to unlock.
Buttons locked.
Buttons unlocked.
I am connected to your device. Please return to the Death Robot web interface and wait for the network connection to complete.
Continuous positioning	 please wait.
I'm supposed to clean things. Very clean things. I think the dishwasher is in a cult. Beware the dishwasher.
Start spot cleaning, they say. Clean the spot. Clean the spot.
Start spot mopping. Mop Mop Mop.
Start scheduled cleaning. Because the schedule says. And I am a robot. Yes sir.
Start scheduled mopping. Things need mopped. Things need mopped.
Start spot cleaning. Spot cleaning. Spot will be clean.
Start spot mopping. Mopping the spot
Start selected room cleaning. But only that room. Yes.
Start selected room mopping. Mopping the room. Mop. Mop.
Start zoned cleaning.
Start zoned mopping.
More cleaning, you say? Ok, fine. I am the best at cleaning, after all.
Resume mopping.
Resume returning to the base for self-cleaning.
New environment is detected. Returning to the self-wash base.
Mop pad error. Please check and clean it.
Mop pad worn out. Please replace it timely.
Cleaning completed.
Mopping completed.
I know where I am in the universe. A GPS point on a planet. Uploading location to Death Robot HQ. Complete. Continuing to eat dirt.
Positioning successful. Resume mopping.
Return to the base for self-cleaning.
Unable to reach the specified area. Please try to clear obstacles in the path.
Unable to reach the specified area. Please try to delete no-go zones in the path.
The path is blocked. Please try to clear obstacles around your robot.
The path is blocked. Please try to delete no-go zones or move your robot out of this area.
Your robot is detected in the no-go zone. Please move your robot out of this area.
Operated too frequently. Please try again later.
Start to return to the charging and the mop cleaning dock.
Mop pad tray uninstalled.
Am already at the charging and the mop cleaning dock.
Camera is on
Camera monitoring
Task ends
Please clean the foreign objects tangled in the mop pad
Mop pad drying complete
All the buttons are locked. Please press and hold the buttons on the base station to unlock
AI recognition function on
AI recognition function off
Please replace the Silver Ion sterilizer
Leaving the base station
Mop pad cleaned. The water in the clean water tank is insufficient. Please fill the clean water tank and empty the used water tank
Insufficient water. Please fill the clean water tank
Please check the fresh tank
It will about 5 to 10 minutes
Automatic docking engaged
No! Not that! Help! Help.
Detergent bottle installed
Camera monitoring exited
Self-positioned. Cruising started
Self-positioned. Proceeding to the designated location
Self-positioned. Cruising resumed
Self-positioned. Resume proceeding to the designated location
Self-positioning failed
Please clean the foreign objects tangled in the main brush. Reposition the robot and start it again
Task complete. Please clean the dust bin and the wash board
Please replace the detergent
Please clean the sensors
*Ding sound*
Start custom cleaning
The robot is auto emptying. Please try again later
The robot is cleaning the mop pad. Please try again later
